        "content": "<p>The revised <a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:editor_manual:progress\">2024 Status and Progress</a>  shows that we now have just about 5 pages left.</p>\n<p>These pages were recently completed:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:routes_tab\">Routes Tab</a> <strong>DONE</strong> Spiv</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:route_properties\">Route Properties</a> <strong>DONE</strong> Spiv 5/29</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:tracks\">Tracks</a> <a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:tracks\">Tab</a><strong>DONE</strong> Mermike</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:track_properties\">Track</a> <a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:track_properties\">Properties</a><strong>DONE</strong> Mermike</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:use_tracks\">Use Tracks</a><strong>DONE</strong> Mermike</p>\n</li>\n<li></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:navigation_data_backup\">Navigation Data Backup</a> <strong>DONE</strong> Rick 5/31</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Just a little more work needed.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:intercommunications\">Intercommunications</a><strong>Good but needs some work</strong> Rick John</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:use_gpx_files\">Use GPX Files</a><strong>Hold</strong> John, Good but <strong>Needs some additional work</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>These are the pages that need more Editing.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:use_routes\">Use Routes</a> <strong>Needs Work</strong> Rick,5/27, Mermike 5/29 split route, 3 minor  Needs integration of new material from route properties.  This needs some reorganization of the examples, other improvements.</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:waypoints_marks_tab\">Waypoint-Marks Tab</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:waypoint_properties\">Waypoint Properties</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:marks\">Use Waypoint Marks</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://opencpn.org/wiki/dokuwiki/doku.php?id=opencpn:manual_basic:route_manager:layers_tab\">Layers Tab</a><strong>Editing</strong> <strong>in progress</strong> sailor1026</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Who will help finish these last few pages, please!</p>\n<p>Thanks,</p>\n<p>Rick</p>",
